# Cloudflare Pages — SPA fallback for the Lastro console.
#
# The console uses react-router (BrowserRouter), so deep links such as
# /lots/:assetId, /audit/:assetId, /process, /chain must all resolve to
# index.html (HTTP 200, no redirect) and let the client router render them.
#
# NOTE: the console also calls a backend at /api/*. When deployed as a static
# site, /api/* must be proxied to the running app server (app/server) or that
# API must be hosted elsewhere; otherwise data calls return this index.html.
# Real build assets under /assets/* are served first and are unaffected.
/*    /index.html    200
